11:14.850 --> 11:16.217
Bad connection.

11:16.217 --> 11:18.153
Ah!

11:18.153 --> 11:19.821
Hello?

11:19.821 --> 11:21.255
Hello?

11:21.255 --> 11:25.059
*

11:25.059 --> 11:26.427
I'm back.

11:26.427 --> 11:27.763
I'm so sorry about that.

11:27.763 --> 11:29.463
That was a little rude.

11:29.463 --> 11:30.765
Where were we?

11:30.765 --> 11:32.033
Kevin, can you tell Glen

11:32.033 --> 11:33.769
I wish I had reached out sooner?

11:33.769 --> 11:34.970
Sure, I wish that

11:34.970 --> 11:36.304
I had reached out sooner.

11:36.304 --> 11:37.905
- You do?
- What? No.

11:37.905 --> 11:39.206
Tell him it came from me.

11:39.206 --> 11:40.808
- It came from me.
- What came from you?

11:40.808 --> 11:42.076
No, tell him that part

11:42.076 --> 11:43.144
came from me.

11:43.144 --> 11:44.211
Part of it came from me.

11:44.211 --> 11:46.014
Which part came from you?

11:46.014 --> 11:47.548
No, tell him Sue.

11:47.548 --> 11:49.051
- Sue.
- I'm sorry,

11:49.051 --> 11:50.751
I'm a little bit lost here.

11:50.751 --> 11:52.254
