11:53.355 --> 11:54.288
Why are you acting weird?

11:54.288 --> 11:56.424
Am I?

11:56.424 --> 11:58.025
I'm sorry, I don't...

11:58.025 --> 12:00.227
You know what, I have a terrible headache

12:00.227 --> 12:01.263
