12:01.263 --> 12:02.397
Oh yeah, of course.

12:02.397 --> 12:03.498
Can I have a lie-down, or... ?

12:03.498 --> 12:04.932
Yes, I totally get it, man.

12:04.932 --> 12:06.134
This has been a big day

12:06.134 --> 12:07.269
for all of us.

12:07.269 --> 12:08.503
- Yeah.
- But I really...

12:08.503 --> 12:10.205
I would love to talk to Sue again.

12:10.205 --> 12:11.306
- I bet.
- Maybe we can

12:11.306 --> 12:13.075
